title: Refactor to adapt m prefix for class member variable
message:
Refactor to adapt m prefix for class member variable

I know most java devs do not use Hungarian notation for variables but
Android code style guide adapt this style. Normally I always uses `this.`
but it does not work in referencing a member variable in an anonymous class.
So I think this prefix style makes code look consistent for member variables.
